              "free_text": [
                "Charged particles were registered using three",
                "telescopes deltaE-E located in the reaction plane. The",
                "intensity of the ionic beam passed through the target",
                "was registered with the help of a Faraday cup connected",
                "to a current integrator."
              ]
            }
